quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  6,132,"And for all there are degrees<i class=""s"">(of rank) </i>according to how <span class=""h"">they<sup foot_note=""80035"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span><span class=""h"">acted</span>, and your<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>Lord is not oblivious of how they act."
  6,133,"Thus your<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>Lord is the Self-Sufficient, the Possessor of mercy. If He wills, He can do away with you<a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>and give succession after you to whomever He wills, just as He initiated you from the offspring of other people."
  6,134,"Indeed, what you are promised is coming, and in no way can you thwart<i class=""s"">(God) </i>."
  6,135,"Say, “O my people, act according to <span class=""h"">your position<sup foot_note=""80036"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>, surely, I am also acting<i class=""s"">(according to mine) </i>; then you will come to know who will have the future outcome of the<i class=""s"">(final) </i>Home. Indeed, the unjust never succeed.”"
  6,136,"And they set aside for Allah a share of the<i class=""s"">(yield of the) </i>fields and the livestock He created, and they said, “This is for Allah,” according to their claim, “and this is for our associates.” But whatever was<i class=""s"">(deemed) </i>for their associates does not reach Allah, yet whatever was<i class=""s"">(deemed) </i>for Allah reaches their associates. Evil is their judgment!"
  6,137,"Likewise, <span class=""h"">their associates have adorned for many polytheists the killing of their children<sup foot_note=""80037"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span>in order to topple them and confound for them their religion. And had Allah willed, they would not have done it, so leave them and what they fabricate."
